articles.title: Suryakumar Yadav Shares BIG Injury Update Following Ankle Concern In Third T20I vs South Africa - Times Now
articles.description: During the third over of the Proteans' run chase, skipper Suryakumar Yadav twisted his ankle while fielding. Earlier in the game, having notched up his fourth T20I hundred, he went level with Rohit Sharma and Glenn Maxwell for the most hundreds in the format.…
